{"id": "1499776637590442185", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "いったんニム毒パ完成…？\n\n超次元倉庫にニム3コス2枚入れといて、リリーバフ、オルライカー極限バフとタイミング合わせて超次元倉庫解放、カウントダウンで行動力2点稼いでバフ持ったニム3コス✖️2で9k毒、狂気解放で7k毒で16k蓄積。後は敵が毒で弱ってくのを眺めるだけ…的な。\n\nボトルネックのオルラとライカーの霊知覚醒札の引き運だけなんとかしたい…！", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T14:16:54.904000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1499776637150171267", "filename": "IMG_7964.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 713239, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1431211464324157450/1499776637150171267/IMG_7964.png?ex=6a33fdd6&is=6a32ac56&hm=0b9c68d935a4f048d1edac631095531f47ce3698808dacb6317dfd1b1afe0964&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499777946658013286", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "核心課題パ！", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T14:22:07.010000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👈", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499779215581773854", "channel_id": "1431211464324157450", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "巻き戻しには葛藤ありつつもう戻れる気がしないという\n\n消去法で一発の銃声にしてますけど、カード3枚引くやつとか25狂気付与の方がいいのか…とも思いつつ。なんかキーオーダーがしっくり来てないです。", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T14:27:09.545000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431211464324157450", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "リリーさんの構成(毒パ)について", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
