{"id": "1499761849934024928", "channel_id": "1448667406687014953", "type": 0, "author_id": "1387651186328469594", "author_name": "nara_mera", "author_bot": false, "content": "この編成のコンセプトはデバフ、シールド、回復で耐久しつつリリーを強化しよう！という編成です", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:18:09.252000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448667406687014953", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "このキャラのここが強い！（対人戦攻略+雑談スレ）", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499762058739187752", "channel_id": "1448667406687014953", "type": 0, "author_id": "1387651186328469594", "author_name": "nara_mera", "author_bot": false, "content": "前から解説します", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:18:59.035000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448667406687014953", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "このキャラのここが強い！（対人戦攻略+雑談スレ）", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499762497933017211", "channel_id": "1448667406687014953", "type": 0, "author_id": "1387651186328469594", "author_name": "nara_mera", "author_bot": false, "content": "・「マーフィー」は盾役です、この3コストのカードをとにかく初めに持ってきたいです。後半にひくと使い所が難しくなります", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:20:43.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:21:10.076000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1499762497690013887", "filename": "IMG_3187.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 975601, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1448667406687014953/1499762497690013887/IMG_3187.png?ex=6a33f0ab&is=6a329f2b&hm=1084b5070991627c75ed3ef8b4132c086e1d4151496095fdde47438c31e65853&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448667406687014953", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "このキャラのここが強い！（対人戦攻略+雑談スレ）", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499763271526256763", "channel_id": "1448667406687014953", "type": 0, "author_id": "1387651186328469594", "author_name": "nara_mera", "author_bot": false, "content": "・「ハムリン」はダメージとデバフ役です。\nモチーフ札を装備した状態で「解放」を打つと全体に大ダメージ、デバフを与えることができます！\n最初は難しいかも知れませんが慣れるとなんでも汎用枠で使いやすいと思います", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:23:48.186000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:31:40.290000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1499763271031324842", "filename": "IMG_3189.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 801518, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1448667406687014953/1499763271031324842/IMG_3189.png?ex=6a33f164&is=6a329fe4&hm=b88b4829a4a95b3191e4de74640fec8be71a4ca037219a3c1a2829d70fe60acb&"}, {"id": "1499763271404752917", "filename": "IMG_3188.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 968530, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1448667406687014953/1499763271404752917/IMG_3188.png?ex=6a33f164&is=6a329fe4&hm=e3d472b2c925de0c7f728189935ffcd67db70fad1df38ccc1364f0a6d9379d12&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448667406687014953", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "このキャラのここが強い！（対人戦攻略+雑談スレ）", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499763583796514846", "channel_id": "1448667406687014953", "type": 0, "author_id": "1387651186328469594", "author_name": "nara_mera", "author_bot": false, "content": "・「シレスト」は回復役です蘇生できたり防御できたり器用なキャラです。デバフは解除出来ないのでそこは注意です！", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:25:02.637000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:31:50.051000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448667406687014953", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "このキャラのここが強い！（対人戦攻略+雑談スレ）", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1499763762788565314", "channel_id": "1448667406687014953", "type": 0, "author_id": "1387651186328469594", "author_name": "nara_mera", "author_bot": false, "content": "・「リリー」防御キャラですが高火力も出すことができる少し変わったキャラです。この編成は先に「導きの帆」を付けます", "timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:25:45.312000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-01T13:26:59.039000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448667406687014953", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "このキャラのここが強い！（対人戦攻略+雑談スレ）", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
